# Obsolete Foundation References

- Treat any references to `foundation/*.md` or `docs/foundation/*.md` as obsolete.
- Do not use those paths as a source of requirements, architecture, or acceptance criteria.
- Prefer current sources in Linear, `docs/adr/`, `docs/product/`, `docs/tech/`, and explicit human comments.
- If an issue depends only on a missing `foundation/*.md` document, ask for clarification instead of inventing requirements.
